en.title: FE Welcomes QP Wearer, Thailand's International Supermodel and Top Movie Actress, Pancake - Kamanit Jamikorn!
en.content: FE is proud to welcome QP Wearer, Thailand's No 1 International Supermodel and Top Movie Actress, Pancake- Kamanit Jamikorn! Pancake very graciously performed 2 songs to an excited FE audience at FE's Thailand Achievers Recognition Dinner at the Grand Convention Hall JJ Mall, Chatuchak, Bangkok on 16th May 2009. The audience absolutely loved Pancake. They surged to the front to take pictures when she appeared on the stage! Thank you, Pancake for gracing our event!
